   - *Description*: Collection of specialized autonomous agents processing specific domains such as health monitoring, financial forecasting, and workflow automation. Maintains persistent memory and reports structured insights.
   - *Source Group Names*: Multi-Agent Intelligence System, System Scheduler & Maintenance
**Component:** `Signal Ingestion & Market Data`
   - *Description*: Gateway for all external data. Parses unstructured signals from Discord and social feeds into structured Levels while providing unified abstraction for real-time and historical price data.
   - *Source Group Names*: Data Ingestion & Signal Parsing, Market Data Infrastructure
**Component:** `Confluence & Decision Engine`
   - *Description*: Core analytical engine synthesizing data from multiple mentors to identify high-probability trade setups. Uses Decision Spine to evaluate confluence across timeframes and strategies.
   - *Source Group Names*: Confluence & Decision Engine
**Component:** `Trading Execution & Safety`
   - *Description*: Manages trade lifecycle including order reconciliation with Tradovate broker and risk management. Includes Chaos Engineering module for fault injection to ensure graceful recovery.
